ee.ria.dhx.ws.service

Interface DhxPackageService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DhxPackageServiceImpl

    public interface DhxPackageService
    Interface for document sending and receiving. Service must be independent from capsule versions that are being sent or received, that means that no changes should be done in service if new capsule version is added.
    Author:
    Aleksei Kokarev

      • receiveDocumentFromEndpoint

        Method is used by endpoint. Is called when document arrives to endpoint.
        Parameters:
        document - - service iniput parameters. document to receive
        client - - SOAP message client(who sent the request).
        service - - SOAP message service(to whom was request sent).
        context - - SOAP message context. If something is missing in parsed objects, then take them from context
        Returns:
        service response
